《'''斯威夫特正义'''》（{{lang-en|''Swift Justice''}}）是[[迪克·沃夫|迪克·沃夫]]和理查德·阿尔巴里诺创作的美国侦破电视剧，于1996年3月13日至7月17日在[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]共播出一季。节目讲述前[[海豹部隊|海豹部隊]]成员麦克·斯威夫特（[[詹姆斯·麥卡菲|詹姆斯·麥卡菲]]饰）被[[纽约市警察局|纽约市警察局]]开除后当上私家侦探，父亲艾尔·斯威夫特（兰·卡琉饰）、过去的警局搭档兰德尔·帕特森警探（[[蓋瑞·杜爾登|蓋瑞·杜爾登]]）都支持他的新事业。电视剧的摄制预算不多，基本是在纽约[[外景拍攝|实地取景]]。

专业评论认为《斯威夫特正义》过分强调暴力，特别是[[電視試播|试播集]]开头的情节，将节目与[[犯罪片|罪案剧情]]电视剧《[[私家侦探_(1985年电视剧)|私家侦探]]》和1988年电影《[[終極警探|終極警探]]》对比。面对观众、广告商和评论家针对暴力镜头的投诉，联合派拉蒙电视网将本剧停播。沃夫认为节目收视率还不错，不该这么快停播。《斯威夫特正义》的视觉呈现和麥卡菲的表演赢得赞誉，但剧评人认为剧情太公式化。

== 构想和人物 ==
《斯威夫特正义》属侦破剧，讲述[[海豹部隊|海豹部隊]]军人麦克·斯威夫特（{{lang|en|Mac Swift}}，[[詹姆斯·麥卡菲|詹姆斯·麥卡菲]]饰）退伍后进入[[纽约市警察局|纽约市警察局]]工作<ref name="Source1">{{cite journal | url = https://variety.com/1996/tv/reviews/swift-justice-1200445322/ | title = Swift Justice | last = Everett | first = Todd | date = 1996-03-12 | journal = [[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] | archive-date = 2018-08-26 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826005229/https://variety.com/1996/tv/reviews/swift-justice-1200445322/ | accessdate = 2020-10-02}}</ref><ref name="Books1">{{cite book | last1 = Brooks | first1 = Tim | last2 = Marsh | first2 = Earle F. | title = The Complete Directory to Prime Time Network and Cable TV Shows, 1946–Present | year = 2009 | publisher = [[兰登书屋|Random House Publishing Group]] | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-345-49773-4}}</ref>，搭档兰德尔·帕特森（{{lang|en|Randall Patterson}}，[[蓋瑞·杜爾登|蓋瑞·杜爾登]]饰）警探正是他最铁的朋友<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source2" />，但麦克的直属上级正好是父亲艾尔·斯威夫特（{{lang|en|Al Swift}}，兰·卡琉饰），和安德鲁·科芬（{{lang|en|Andrew Coffin}}，[[詹卡洛·埃斯波西托|詹卡洛·埃斯波西托]]饰）等其他领导都经常训斥麦克<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Books1" /><ref name="Source2">{{Cite news | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826005243/https://www.nytimes.com/1996/03/13/arts/television-review-sort-of-like-batman-with-uzis-and-laptops.html | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | archive-date = 2018-08-26 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1996/03/13/arts/television-review-sort-of-like-batman-with-uzis-and-laptops.html | title = Television Review: Sort of Like Batman, With Uzis and Laptops | last = O'Connor | first = John J. | date = 1996-03-13 | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]]}}</ref>。麦克在[[電視試播|试播集]]中想要逮捕[[性交易|卖淫团伙]]的幕后黑手（[[斯基普·萨德思|斯基普·萨德思]]饰），此人还利用妓女制造[[甜蜜陷阱|甜蜜陷阱]]，勒索、贩毒和信用卡信息盗窃都有涉足<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source2" />。麦克为破案与妓女安妮（[[金·迪肯斯|金·迪肯斯]]）合作，两人逐渐产生感情，她是为支付大学学费和母亲的养老院费用走上卖淫之路<ref name="Source1" />。安妮遭人谋杀后，麦克的行为变得越来越乖张和暴力<ref name="Source2" />，最终导致他在试播集结尾被警局解职<ref name="Source1" />。

麦克在后面的分集中成为[[私家侦探|私家侦探]]，向那些因“常规执法原则所限无法获得帮助”的人服务<ref name="Books1" />。他不动用私刑，而是设法提升客户走上法庭的胜算<ref name="Source3">{{cite news | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | url = https://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1996-03-13-9603130217-story.html | title = The Formula: Debut Of UPN's 'Swift Justice' Built Around Several Conventional Ideas | last = Johnson | first = Steve | date = 1996-03-13 | newspaper = [[芝加哥論壇報|Chicago Tribune]] | archive-date = 2018-10-03 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181003101722/http://www.chicagotribune.com/news/ct-xpm-1996-03-13-9603130217-story.html}}</ref>。麦克精通计算机<ref name="Books1" />，单靠设计软件的[[版稅|版稅]]收入就足以保障财务稳定<ref name="Source1" />，还设立电子邮件地址接受客户来信<ref name="Books1" />。据[[联合派拉蒙电视网|联合派拉蒙电视网]]宣传，麦克依靠“科技、智慧、魅力和肌肉”破案<ref name="Source4">{{cite news | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190219045540/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1996-03-13/lifestyle/9603110389_1_swift-justice-meredith-baxter-swift-falls | title = New Shows: Flat, Flashy And Lousy | archivedate = 2019-02-19 | url = https://www.orlandosentinel.com/news/os-xpm-1996-03-13-9603110389-story.html | last = Boedeker | first = Hal | date = 1996-03-13 | newspaper = Orlando Sentinel | deadurl = no}}</ref>，是20世纪“90年代真正的技术主导型犯罪斗士”<ref name="Source2" />。兰德尔在全季经常向麦克提供案件信息，艾尔被降职，从外勤警官变成办公室警员<ref name="Books1" />。

部分分集涉及的案件包括：[[摇滚乐|摇滚]]歌手想与家暴丈夫离婚而不可得；夫妻离婚后儿子和母亲生活，但却被父亲绑架；男子将受害人绑起来折磨，把高尔夫球朝他们身上打<ref name="Books1" /><ref name="Source4" />。[[客串|客串]]出镜的明星包括[[珍妮佛·嘉納|珍妮佛·嘉納]]<ref name="2019NewSources2">{{cite journal | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | url = https://ew.com/gallery/law-and-order-guest-stars/?slide=258020#258020 | title = Law & Order: 30 Best Guest Stars | last = Boardman | first = Madeline | date = 2016-06-22 | journal = [[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200407133339/https://ew.com/gallery/law-and-order-guest-stars/ | archive-date = 2020-04-07 | deadurl = no}}</ref>和[[德瑞·德·玛泰|德瑞·德·玛泰]]（{{lang|en|Drea de Matteo}}）<ref name="2019NewSources1">{{cite news | url = https://www.cbsnews.com/news/drea-de-matteos-sexy-bad-girl/ | title = Drea de Matteo's Sexy Bad Girl | last = Morales | first = Tatiana | publisher = [[CBS新聞|CBS News]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190423040908/https://www.cbsnews.com/news/drea-de-matteos-sexy-bad-girl/ | date = 2005-01-28 | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | archive-date = 2019-04-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>和[[Ice-T|Ice-T]]<ref name="IceBooks">{{cite book | last1 = Ice-T | last2 = Century | first2 = Douglas | title = Ice: A Memoir of Gangster Life and Redemption-- from South Central to Hollywood | year = 2012 | publisher = Ballantine Books | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-345-52329-7 | page = 159}}</ref>。许多评论员认为本剧过于暴力<ref name="Source2" /><ref name="SourceTDN">{{cite news | deadurl = no | url = https://www.deseret.com/1996/3/13/19230458/faculty-is-too-dumb-swift-is-too-violent | title = 'Faculty' is Too Dumb, 'Swift' is Too Violent | last = Pierce | first = Scott D. | date = 1996-03-13 | newspaper = The Deseret News | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826043851/https://www.deseretnews.com/article/477158/FACULTY-IS-TOO-DUMB-SWIFT-IS-TOO-VIOLENT.html | archive-date = 2018-08-26 | accessdate = 2020-10-03}}</ref><ref name="SourceSFG2">{{cite news | newspaper = [[旧金山纪事报|San Francisco Chronicle]] | first = John | last = Carman | url = https://www.sfgate.com/news/article/JOHN-CARMAN-on-TELEVISION-UPN-s-Justice-2990534.php | title = UPN's 'Justice' Arrives With A Splatter | date = 1996-03-13 | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | deadurl = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826005221/https://www.sfgate.com/news/article/JOHN-CARMAN-on-TELEVISION-UPN-s-Justice-2990534.php | archive-date = 2018-08-26}}</ref>，特别是试播集开头就有九人死亡<ref name="SourceTDN" />。虽然暴力镜头很多，但剧中却没有鲜血四溅的场面<ref name="PlotHoles">{{Cite news | url = https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1996-03-13-ca-46373-story.html | title = 'Faculty' Short on Laughs; 'Justice' Is Long on Holes | last = Rosenberg | first = Howard | date = 1996-03-13 | newspaper = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180825235235/http://articles.latimes.com/1996-03-13/entertainment/ca-46373_1_swift-justice | archive-date = 2018-08-25 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-10-03}}</ref>。部分剧评将《斯威夫特正义》与[[犯罪片|罪案剧情电视剧]]《[[私家侦探_(1985年电视剧)|私家侦探]]》''{{lang|en|The Equalizer}}''和1988年电影[[動作片|動作片]]《[[終極警探|終極警探]]》对比<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="Source2" /><ref name="Source3" />，《[[奥兰多哨兵报|奥兰多哨兵报]]》（''{{lang|en|Orlando Sentinel}}''）的哈尔·博德克（{{lang|en|Hal Boedeker}}）认为新剧属“都市[[西部作品|西部电视剧]]”<ref name="Source4" />。主创兼执行制作人[[迪克·沃夫|迪克·沃夫]]觉得主人翁就像“不戴面具的[[蝙蝠俠|蝙蝠俠]]”<ref name="Source2" />，节目基调反[[政治正確|政治正確]]而行之<ref name="SourceUPN">{{cite web | url = https://interviews.televisionacademy.com/shows/swift-justice | title = Dick Wolf on producing Swift Justice | date = 2013-01-10 | publisher = Academy of Television Arts & Sciences | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200619180200/https://interviews.televisionacademy.com/shows/swift-justice | archive-date = 2020-06-19 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-10-03}}</ref>。他根据1957年开播的电视剧《[[枪手圣骑士|枪手圣骑士]]》（''{{lang|en|Have Gun – Will Travel}}''）中的主人翁创作人物麦克<ref name="ShootingSource1">{{cite web | archivedate = 2019-04-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190422135431/https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1996-03-13-9603110431-story.html | url = https://www.sun-sentinel.com/news/fl-xpm-1996-03-13-9603110431-story.html | title = Shooting at the V-Chip | last = Jicha | first = Tom | date = 1996-03-13 | newspaper = Sun-Sentinel | accessdate = 2020-10-03}}</ref>，觉得麦克与兰德尔的友谊就像《[[致命武器|致命武器]]》系列电影中的[[马丁·瑞格|马丁·瑞格]]（{{lang|en|Martin Riggs}}）和[[罗杰·默托|罗杰·默托]]（{{lang|en|Roger Murtaugh}}）<ref name="SourceNYD">{{cite news | archive-date = 2018-08-26 | deadurl = no | url = https://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/show-swift-ly-sets-tone-article-1.719782 | title = Cop Show 'Swift'-ly Sets Its Tone | last = Mink | first = Eric | newspaper = [[紐約每日新聞|New York Daily News]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826005100/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/entertainment/show-swift-ly-sets-tone-article-1.719782 | date = 1996-03-12 | accessdate = 2020-10-03}}</ref><ref name="SourceCSM">{{cite news | url = https://www.csmonitor.com/1996/0312/12141.html | title = Worth Noting on TV | last = Nichols | first = Judy | date = 1996-03-12 | newspaper = [[基督科学箴言报|The Christian Science Monitor]] | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826005118/https://www.csmonitor.com/1996/0312/12141.html | archive-date = 2018-08-26 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 制作与播映 ==
[[File:DickWolfJan10.jpg|thumb]]是《斯威夫特正义》的主创兼执行制作人]]

《斯威夫特正义》由[[迪克·沃夫|沃夫影业]]与[[环球电视公司|环球电视公司]]制作，沃夫和理查德·阿尔巴里诺（{{lang|en|Richard Albarino}}）主创<ref name="Source1" /><ref name="SourceNecessity">{{cite web | archive-date = 2019-02-20 | deadurl = yes | url = http://opsis.georgetown.edu/articles/PerformingTheLaw.html | title = The Necessity of Spectacle Events in the Legislative and Judicial Processes | last = Spielmann | first = Guy | date = 2014 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190220002808/http://opsis.georgetown.edu/articles/PerformingTheLaw.html | publisher = [[乔治城大学|Georgetown University]] | accessdate = 2019-02-20}}</ref>。节目是在纽约[[外景拍攝|实地取景]]<ref name="Source1" />，《[[紐約_(雜誌)|纽约]]》杂志的莫琳·卡拉汉（{{lang|en|Maureen Callahan}}）称本剧制作成本很低<ref name="SourceJournal1">{{cite journal | last = Callahan | first = Maureen | date = 1996-04-22 | title = Life Intimidates Art | journal = [[紐約_(雜誌)|New York]] | volume = 29 | issue = 16 | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=M-ECAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA18&dq=%22Swift+Justice%22+%22UPN%22&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=%22Swift%20Justice%22%20%22UPN%22&f=false | deadurl = no | page = 18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180825125425/https://books.google.com/books?id=M-ECAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA18&dq=%22Swift+Justice%22+%22UPN%22&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwiFwPjAj4fdAhUuwlkKHepmBjwQ6AEIRzAG#v=onepage&q=%22Swift%20Justice%22%20%22UPN%22&f=false | archive-date = 2018-08-25}}</ref>。拍摄期间，在剧中客串出演诈骗犯的[[让-克洛德·拉马雷|让-克洛德·拉马雷]]（{{lang|en|Jean-Claude La Marre}}）差点被警员逮捕，拉马雷声称警方[[种族归纳|凭种族偏见抓人]]，制片商和纽约市警察局对此不予置评<ref name="SourceJournal1" />。托德·埃弗里特（{{lang|en|Todd Everett}}）在《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|综艺]]》杂志发文，称里克·马洛塔（{{lang|en|Rick Marotta}}）创作的合成打击器乐表现不俗<ref name="Source1" />。《斯威夫特正义》是[[加里·格拉斯伯格|加里·格拉斯伯格]]（{{lang|en|Gary Glasberg}}）首度为剧长约一小时的电视节目编剧，自认属“重大突破”，他后来成为侦破剧《[[重返犯罪現場|海军罪案调查处]]》的[[節目統籌|節目統籌]]<ref name="2019NewSources3">{{cite journal | url = https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/showrunners-2012-ncis-gary-glasberg-shane-brennan-375978 | title = Showrunners 2012 'NCIS' Gary Glasberg and 'NCIS Los Angeles' Shane Brennan | last = Guthrie | first = Marisa | date = 2012-10-03 | journal = [[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]] | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190423034050/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/showrunners-2012-ncis-gary-glasberg-shane-brennan-375978 | archive-date = 2019-04-23 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

联合派拉蒙电视网制订“新春激进节目单”，将电视台的节目时段增至每周三个晚上<ref name="Source3" />，并为此订购《斯威夫特正义》作为季中换血节目<ref name="HighBeam11">{{cite news | accessdate = 2018-11-18 | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-17254139.html | title = From fighting cavities to fighting V-chips.(Richard Wolf goes from advertising copywriter to screenwriter) | last = Coe | first = Steve | date = 1995-08-28 | work = Broadcasting & Cable | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181118180330/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-17254139.html | archive-date = 2018-11-18 | deadurl = yes}}{{subscription required}}</ref>，占据[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]周三晚九点档<ref name="Books1" />，1996年3至7月共播出13集<ref name="SourceTVGuide1">{{cite journal | url = https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/swift-justice/episodes/204736/ | title = Episode Guide | journal = [[电视指南_(美国杂志)|TV Guide]] | archive-date = 2018-08-26 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-10-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826005244/https://www.tvguide.com/tvshows/swift-justice/episodes/204736/}}</ref>。《[[落基山新闻报|落基山新闻报]]》（''{{lang|en|Rocky Mountain News}}''）刊登达斯提·桑德斯（{{lang|en|Dusty Saunders}}）的文章，称本剧证明联合派拉蒙电视网的节目正朝[[動作片|动作历险类]]转变<ref name="HighBeam1">{{Cite news | url = https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-67765928.html | title = Quasi-Network UPN Moving into Action-Adventure Arena | last = Saunders | first = Dusty | date  =1996-03-20 | newspaper = Rocky Mountain News | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181120135333/https://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-67765928.html | archive-date = 2018-11-20 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2018-11-20}}{{subscription required}}</ref>。斯科蒂·杜普里（{{lang|en|Scotty Dupree}}）在《[[媒体周刊|媒体周刊]]》（''{{lang|en|Mediaweek}}''）发文，认为本剧与《[[哨兵_(电视剧)|哨兵]]》（''{{lang|en|The Sentinel}}''）均旨在吸收男观众，其中《斯威夫特正义》是除《[[执法悍将|执法悍将]]》以外周三晚唯一主要面向男观众的节目<ref name="SourceTrove">{{Cite journal | last = Dupree | first = Scotty | date = 1996-03-04 | title = UPN aims for boys' night in; Wednesday now a six-way race | url = https://trove.nla.gov.au/work/58655015?q&versionId=71664428 | deadurl = yes | journal = Mediaweek | volume = v6 | issue = n10 | page = 8(1) | archive-date = 2018-08-26 | access-date = 2018-08-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180826043913/https://trove.nla.gov.au/work/58655015?q&versionId=71664428}}</ref>。对此沃夫也表示，电视剧的目标观众群是18至34岁男子<ref name="2019NewSources5">{{cite news | url = https://scholar.lib.vt.edu/VA-news/VA-Pilot/issues/1996/vp960313/03130042.htm | title = UPN's Cool Rogue Cop Beats Laughable 'JAG' | last = Bonko | first = Larry | date = 1996-03-13 | newspaper = The Virginian-Pilot | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190219045540/https://scholar.lib.vt.edu/VA-news/VA-Pilot/issues/1996/vp960313/03130042.htm | archivedate = 2019-02-19 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2020-10-03}}</ref>。

